WEBVTT

00:00.290 --> 00:03.953
Here are some phrases you can use when saying you are sorry.

00:05.795 --> 00:07.522
I am sorry.

00:09.367 --> 00:10.627
I apologize.

00:12.537 --> 00:13.705
That's my fault.

00:15.600 --> 00:16.725
Please forgive me.

00:18.517 --> 00:19.418
My bad.

00:21.403 --> 00:22.970
Please don't be angry.

00:24.637 --> 00:26.857
I'm really ashamed of myself.

00:28.619 --> 00:30.508
How inconsiderate of me.

00:32.495 --> 00:34.489
Please accept my apologies.

00:36.218 --> 00:38.479
What can I do for you to forgive me?

